    "glp1_mechanism": {
      "type": "rich-text",
      "blocks": {
        "caption": {
          "type": "caption",
          "settings": {
            "caption": "First, a calm explanation",
            "text_style": "caption-with-letter-spacing"
          }
        },
        "text": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>When the body goes through rapid weight loss, more hairs than usual can temporarily shift into their natural resting-and-shedding phase, and eating less can mean fewer of the nutrients hair depends on. It is common, it is usually temporary, and nutrition is one thing you can actively support.*</p>"
          }
        },
        "pullquote": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><em>This is not about doing more. It is about giving your hair the building blocks it may be missing right now.</em></p>"
          }
        }
      },
